1. Broj slučajeva zaraze koronavirusom rapidno raste. (*slučajeva* - Nominative case) (The number of coronavirus infections is rapidly increasing.)

2. Ovo je samo jedan od slučajeva kada je bila potrebna hitna intervencija lekara. (*slučajeva* - Genitive case) (This is just one of the cases where urgent medical intervention was needed.)

3. U ovoj oblasti, postoje mnogi slučajevi zloupotrebe vlasti. (*slučajevi* - Nominative case) (In this field, there are many cases of abuse of power.)

4. Nisam siguran da li je u ovom slučaju reč o kršenju zakona. (*slučaju* - Dative case) (I'm not sure if this case involves a violation of the law.)

5. Molim vas da pažljivo pročitate uputstvo i pratite korake u slučaju da se pojave neželjena dejstva. (*slučaju* - Locative case) (Please read the instructions carefully and follow the steps in case of any unwanted effects.)